.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, lemonade, mirinda, tea
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: november, august, june, october, september, february, july
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, disco, indie, metal, pop, reggae, rock
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, car, helicopter, quad-bike, roller, ship, skateboard
 1. the person drinking cola is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the fan of rock is the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the fan of metal is between the fan of indie and the person who's birthday is in july##2
11. the fan of disco is the person who's birthday is in october##1
12. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
13. the fan of pop is between the person who's birthday is in july and the fan of reggae##2
14. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
15. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the car##1
16. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
17. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
18. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
19. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
20. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person driving the ship and the person who's birthday is in august##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |     4      |    5    |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | hot-chocolate | 7up      | iced-tea   | tea     | mirinda    | cola      |
